Prerequisite :
1VM - ubuntu - 2Vcpu and 2GiB
Install terraform on Vm1 - ansible
Create a new VM using terraform - ansible <ip and host file>
Install Docker on Vm2 - ansible
Install terrafrom on Vm2 - ansible
Use terraform on VM2 to create a container on VM2 - using Vm1 - ansible
create a job in jenkins to accomodate all of these above tasks - vm1

Problem statement :
Containerize Nginx service.

Condition :
Nothing should be done on 1VM. 1VM can only be used to leverage tools.
